{"url": "https://people.com/royals/meghan-markle-speech-royal-wedding-reception/", "text": "The newly minted Duchess of Sussex is ready to address her people.\n\nMeghan Markle will give a speech at the evening reception Saturday celebrating her marriage to Prince Harry. Following months of speculation that the actress, 36, would break protocol and address guests on her wedding day, Kensington Palace confirmed that Markle will do exactly that at Frogmore House party on Saturday night. Approximately 200 friends and family members are expected to be present at the celebration hosted by Prince Charles.\n\n\u201cMs. Markle will speak at the Evening Reception,\u201d the palace confirmed.\n\nHarry spoke to attendees earlier at the lunch reception hosted by Queen Elizabeth at Windsor Castle\u2019s St. George\u2019s Hall.\n\nWatch our full special, Meghan and Harry \u2013 a Fairy-Tale Wedding, on PeopleTV, now available on PeopleTV.com and on your favorite streaming device.\n\nIt\u2019s the event of the year! Be sure to keep up with all of PEOPLE\u2019s royal wedding coverage and don\u2019t forget to check out everything you need to know about Meghan Markle\u2019s perfect style.\n\nRELATED VIDEO: Harry and Meghan\u2019s Love Story\n\n\u201cIt was very off-the-cuff, which was lovely,\u201d a guest tells PEOPLE of the prince\u2019s speech. \u201cHe promised that all the Americans wouldn\u2019t steal the swords and said, \u2018Please, when you leave, be quiet as you don\u2019t want to wake the neighbors,\u2019 which was quite fun.\u201d\n\nThe 33-year-old received massive cheers from the approximately 600 people in attendance Saturday when he mentioned \u201cmy wife and I\u201d as he thanked all the guests.\n\nPrince Harry and Meghan Markle. Ben Birchall/PA Wire\n\n\u201cIt was more than you would ever imagine it to be,\u201d the guest adds. \u201cIt did feel like we were really part of their very special occasion. It just felt about the two of them, which was great.\u201d\n\nHarry\u2019s dad, Prince Charles, also gave a speech at Saturday afternoon\u2019s affair. \u201cHe ended it calling him, \u2018My darling old Harry, I\u2019m so happy for you,\u2019 which was very sweet,\u201d the guest continues, adding that Charles also commented on \u201chow he\u2019s really happy for them both.\u201d", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/NhdNpuM3lBYdt3kwYz3lderqD3U=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Meghan-Duchess-of-Sussex-attends-the-2025-TIME100-Summit-Meghan-Markle-Debuts-Royal-Monogram-103025-363e33a03f144a7bb5b0867009bd1320.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/ZvAhd1PP9kO8x1nmx6CeYcy_3YA=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Queen-Elizabeth-Prince-Philip-wedding-1-jpg-cbe332a4d2d0478eb4d1827f590aa3a4.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/k2MVcpPRLlF0coL7S6yFEwfocMw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/prince-harry-meghan-markle-110725-bdaa13e8ec84464a88ae53b8344cbde0.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/26_J2fAXIKk0V705Qyb0Cs44ois=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/meghan-markle-prince-harry-1-111325-07ba1342d900451385e988735fb1cf84.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/-TxNVmJuZnFGAM9RVIMlX-BNIsc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Queen-Camilla-Princess-Eugenie-111825-a9937b17e33249388f14a292b9a2b361.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/ndGj_BD1Phe2JRQ16KwMkPjWexU=/343x228/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/kate-middleton-prince-william-engagement-anniversary-111622-2-b707145a44ef41d9904ddff59c1e8f2a.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/PygNhhf52DDmEMnGYs3AYWlcK6k=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/queen-camilla-king-charles-prince-william-catherine-princess-of-wales-the-diplomatic-reception-111425-1-b87bf11df7554406ad661cd40d11ce72.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/9Z7M2eS2QzCl3ydKWxa63X4_6LM=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Meghan-Markle-Harpers-Bazaar-111925-1-9ac00a98ff4845cca2412066a1488a91